column4: Euro notes and coins introduced and replace Deutsche Mark as currency
Joseph Cardinal Ratzinger (b. 1927) becomes Pope Benedict XVI
2009 elections; Merkel begins to head a centre-right government of the CDU\/CSU and FDP.[26]
2013 elections; Merkel heads a centre-right grand coalition of the CDU\/CSU and SPD.
German national football team wins Football World Cup
